  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de chrpath</title>

    <para>
      Installez <application>chrpath</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes :
       
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> :
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make docdir=/usr/share/doc/&chrpath-version; install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

